metadata.name: Buffed Santa #6602
metadata.description: The Buffed Santa Club is a collection featuring 8.888 buffed Santas on the Ethereum blockchain. These Santas have had enough cookies and have decided to hit the gym and get buffed. Each Buffed Santa NFT is a collectible digital asset that represents a unique, hand-drawn NFT. Whether you are a die-hard fitness enthusiast or just looking for something fun and festive, the Buffed Santa Club has something for everyone.The collection has a public domain license and is inspired by Bored Ape Yacht Club and GigaChad Yacht Club.No Bullshit.No roadmap.Just Santas.
